title: SOLD Obak T212-2 150 Subj. Brackenridge Mais Paper Wrapper

posts.post_title: SOLD Obak T212-2 150 Subj. Brackenridge Mais Paper Wrapper
posts.post_content: I finally finished my slogan run and I ended up with this dupe that needs a home. This card has lots going on with it. First, PSA mislabeled it 1911.....no comment. Second, it's a 150 subject, if you're into that kind of thing. Third, MPW is one of the hardest slogans to find. Obvious creasing, but the corners aren't horrible and there's tons of original gloss. $50 dlvd
